metadata.name: Art of Body 1
metadata.description:
My 1/10 limited NFT of "Art of Body" collection. 

Hand drawn by me. 
1622 x 1794

When I drew this NFT, I was very inspired by the process.
I wanted to breathe some life into the drawing, and I hope I succeeded. My Art is not the application of a canon of beauty, but just my view of women body
hand drawn by me.
